<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
  <div rend="parallel">
      <p xml:id="Aink206-kilavi"> iravukkuṟikkaṇ ṭalaimakaṉ vantu kuṟiyiṭattu niṉṟamai yaṟinta tōḻi talaimakaṭkuc colliyatu.</p>
      <p xml:lang="en"> What the confidante, aware that the hero had arrived at the night meeting-place and stood at the meeting place, said to the heroine. </p>
      </div>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="Aink206">
<l>aṉṉāy vāḻivēṇ ṭaṉṉai yuvakkāṇ</l>
<l>mārik kuṉṟattuk kāppā ḷaṉṉa</l>
<l>tūvali ṉaṉainta toṭalai yoḷvāṭ</l>
<l>pāci cūḻnta peruṅkaḻaṟ</l>
<l>ṟaṇpaṉi vaikiya varikkac ciṉaṉē</l>
      </lg>

<lg xml:lang="en">
<l> Oh Mother, please Mother, </l>

<l rend="space">look there </l>
<l rend="space indent">at him with the striped girdle where cool dew rests, </l>
<l rend="indent">[with] big anklets beset by lichen </l>
<l rend="indent">and a sword bright [like] a wreath dampened by raindrops,</l>
<l rend="space">[who] resembles the guardian of the rainy mountain. </l>

      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
